    <section id="career" data-screen-label="Career" style="padding:clamp(80px,12vh,150px) clamp(24px,5vw,84px);">
      <span data-anim="fm-rise" style="opacity:0;display:block;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.28em;color:#FF9E80;margin-bottom:8px;">03 — CAREER</span>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:clamp(10px,2vw,28px);flex-wrap:wrap;margin:0 0 clamp(36px,6vh,64px);"><h2 data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="100" style="opacity: 0; margin: 0; font-family: 'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(34px,5vw,68px); line-height: 1.2; color: #1E3A8A; position: relative">回り道でも、ええ感じ。</h2><img src="shirankedo.png" alt="しらんけど" class="fm-jerk1" style="width:clamp(96px,15vw,180px);height:auto;flex-shrink:0;margin-bottom:clamp(4px,0.8vw,12px);filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 14px rgba(15,23,42,0.1));pointer-events:none;"></div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
        <div data-anim="fm-rise" style="opacity:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:90px 1fr;gap:clamp(14px,3vw,48px);align-items:start;border-top:1px solid rgba(30,58,138,0.12);padding:28px 0;">
          <span style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#FF9E80;">CH.01</span>
          <div data-col2="" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.4fr;gap:clamp(10px,2vw,40px);align-items:baseline;">
            <h3 style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(17px,1.7vw,22px);color:#1E3A8A;">元々は観光学部出身でした</h3>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:clamp(12px,1vw,14px);line-height:1.85;color:rgba(15,23,42,0.7);">コロナ禍で、行きたかった業界がまさかの全滅。落ち込むヒマもなく就活は続く。「しゃーないし、違う業界に行ってみよ」と心機一転。未経験で飛び込んだ業界で待ち受けていたのは、深い深いデザインの沼でした。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="80" style="opacity:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:90px 1fr;gap:clamp(14px,3vw,48px);align-items:start;border-top:1px solid rgba(30,58,138,0.12);padding:28px 0;">
          <span style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#FF9E80;">CH.02</span>
          <div data-col2="" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.4fr;gap:clamp(10px,2vw,40px);align-items:baseline;">
            <h3 style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(17px,1.7vw,22px);color:#1E3A8A;">大手上場企業に就職</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(12px,1vw,14px); line-height: 1.85; color: rgba(15,23,42,0.7); position: relative">がむしゃらに食らいついて、2年目で本社異動。大手上場企業のECサイトにデザイン・制作担当として携わり、現場で０からデザインに関する知識を鍛えました。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="160" style="opacity:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:90px 1fr;gap:clamp(14px,3vw,48px);align-items:start;border-top:1px solid rgba(30,58,138,0.12);padding:28px 0;">
          <span style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#FF9E80;">CH.03</span>
          <div data-col2="" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.4fr;gap:clamp(10px,2vw,40px);align-items:baseline;">
            <h3 style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(17px,1.7vw,22px);color:#1E3A8A;">心機一転、ベンチャー企業へ</h3>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:clamp(12px,1vw,14px);line-height:1.85;color:rgba(15,23,42,0.7);">そんな中、「もっとデザインを極めたい」と思うようになり、そんな中「うちの会社でデザイナーをしてほしい！」と声がかかり、「これはもう伸びしろしかないやろ」と、迷う暇もなく一念発起で退社。畑違いのベンチャーへ体当たりし、無我夢中で勉強。覚えたことは、ぜんぶ会社に還元しました。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="240" style="opacity:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:90px 1fr;gap:clamp(14px,3vw,48px);align-items:start;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,158,128,0.5);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,158,128,0.5);padding:28px 0;background:rgba(255,158,128,0.05);border-radius:0 0 18px 18px;">
          <span style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#FF9E80;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;"><span style="width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#FF9E80;"></span>NOW</span>
          <div data-col2="" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.4fr;gap:clamp(10px,2vw,40px);align-items:baseline;">
            <h3 style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(18px,1.9vw,24px);color:#1E3A8A;">デザインチーム責任者</h3>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:clamp(12px,1vw,14px);line-height:1.85;color:rgba(15,23,42,0.78);">今ではチームを引っ張りつつ、メンバーの成長にも伴走中です。その上で、お客さんにとことん寄り添い、「なんか、めっちゃええ感じ。」と思ってもらえるように尽力中。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section><div style="overflow:hidden;background:#1E3A8A;padding:16px 0;transform:rotate(0.8deg);margin:0 -6vw 0 0;">
      <div style="display:flex;width:max-content;animation:fm-marquee-rev 26s linear infinite;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:30px;padding-right:30px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(15px,1.8vw,24px);color:#fff;white-space:nowrap;"><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>話しやすさ、ピカイチ</span><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>とことん寄り添う</span><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>「なんか、めっちゃええ感じやん。」</span><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>返信、めっちゃ早い</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:30px;padding-right:30px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(15px,1.8vw,24px);color:#fff;white-space:nowrap;"><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>話しやすさ、ピカイチ</span><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>とことん寄り添う</span><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>「思てたより、ええやん！」</span><span style="color:#FF9E80;">●</span><span>返信、めっちゃ早い</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- WHY -->
    <section id="why" data-screen-label="Why Me" style="padding: clamp(80px,12vh,150px) clamp(24px,5vw,84px); position: relative">
      <span data-anim="fm-rise" style="opacity:0;display:block;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.28em;color:#FF9E80;margin-bottom:8px;">04 — WHY ME</span>
      <h2 data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="100" style="opacity: 0; margin: 0 0 clamp(36px,6vh,64px); font-family: 'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(34px,5vw,68px); line-height: 1.2; color: #1E3A8A; position: relative">選んでもらえる、<span style="color:#FF9E80;">3つ</span>のワケ。</h2>
      <div data-col3="" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:clamp(16px,2vw,28px);">
        
        <div data-anim="fm-rise" style="opacity:0;position:relative;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(31,38,135,0.06);border-radius:26px;padding:clamp(24px,2.6vw,40px);overflow:hidden;min-height:240px;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;position:relative;">
            <span class="fm-why-num" style="font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #FF9E80">01</span>
            <span class="fm-why-en" style="font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(12px,1.3vw,16px); letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(30,58,138,0.32); opacity: 0.5">SUGGESTION</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="fm-why-h" style="margin:18px 0 12px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(17px,1.6vw,21px);color:#1E3A8A;position:relative;">寄り添う提案力</h3>
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:13px;line-height:1.95;color:rgba(15,23,42,0.75);position:relative;">とことんヒアリングして、お客さん自身も気づいてない「ほんまの課題」を言語化。貪欲さと、おもてなしの精神で、期待のナナメ上までご提案します。</p>
        </div><div data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="130" style="opacity:0;position:relative;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(31,38,135,0.06);border-radius:26px;padding:clamp(24px,2.6vw,40px);overflow:hidden;min-height:240px;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;position:relative;">
            <span class="fm-why-num" style="font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #FF9E80">02</span>
            <span class="fm-why-en" style="font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(12px,1.3vw,16px); letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(30,58,138,0.32); opacity: 0.5">APPROACHABLE</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="fm-why-h" style="margin:18px 0 12px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(17px,1.6vw,21px);color:#1E3A8A;position:relative;">早いレスポンスと、関西人らしい親しみやすさ</h3>
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:13px;line-height:1.95;color:rgba(15,23,42,0.75);position:relative;">返信が早く、そして初対面でも話しやすい。専門用語で煙に巻いたりしません。「めっちゃ気軽に相談できるやん」と、思ってもらえる距離感を大事にしてます。</p>
        </div>
        <div data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="260" style="opacity:0;position:relative;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(31,38,135,0.06);border-radius:26px;padding:clamp(24px,2.6vw,40px);overflow:hidden;min-height:240px;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;position:relative;">
            <span class="fm-why-num" style="font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #FF9E80">03</span>
            <span class="fm-why-en" style="font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(12px,1.3vw,16px); letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(30,58,138,0.32); opacity: 0.5">AMBITION</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="fm-why-h" style="margin:18px 0 12px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(17px,1.6vw,21px);color:#1E3A8A;position:relative;">止まらない向上心</h3>
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:13px;line-height:1.95;color:rgba(15,23,42,0.75);position:relative;">新しい分野や環境にも「めっちゃおもろそう！」で飛び込むタイプです。いつも何かしら勉強中で、ツールも知識も日々アップデートしながら、これからもクオリティを磨き続けます。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SKILLS -->
    

    <!-- CONTACT -->
    <section id="skills" data-screen-label="Skills" style="padding: clamp(80px,12vh,150px) clamp(24px,5vw,84px); position: relative">
      <span data-anim="fm-rise" style="opacity: 0; display: block; font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; color: #FF9E80; margin-bottom: 8px; position: relative">05 — SKILLS &amp; LICENSE</span>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:clamp(10px,2vw,28px);flex-wrap:wrap;margin:0 0 clamp(36px,6vh,64px);"><h2 data-anim="fm-rise" data-rd="100" style="opacity: 0; margin: 0; font-family: 'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(34px,5vw,68px); line-height: 1.2; color: #1E3A8A; position: relative">つくれるもの。</h2><img src="paint.png" alt="パレット" class="fm-jerk2" style="width:clamp(104px,16vw,190px);height:auto;flex-shrink:0;margin-bottom:clamp(4px,0.8vw,12px);filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 14px rgba(15,23,42,0.1));pointer-events:none;"></div>

